 
<p>

  <a class=glossary href="/glossary.html#global%20heating">Global heating</a> is <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/global-development/2023/apr/18/andes-community-devastated-by-climate-crisis-quelccaya-glacier-peru">wiping out ancient settlements in the high Andes</a>
because there is no more water.

 